jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/FrankCarter-and-Sex-Pistols-Kentish-Town-London-show-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/FrankCarter-and-Sex-Pistols-Kentish-Town-London-show-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/FrankCarter-and-Sex-Pistols-Kentish-Town-London-show-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/FrankCarter-and-Sex-Pistols-Kentish-Town-London-show-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/FrankCarter-and-Sex-Pistols-Kentish-Town-London-show-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sex-pistols">Sex Pistols</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/frank-carter">Frank Carter</a>开始了他们在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/heres-what-sex-pistols-and-frank-carter-played-at-londons-bush-hall-3783522">Bush Hall 的演出</a>，并将歌词改为经典曲目“God Save The Queen”。看看下面的内容，以及他们在<a href="/artists/yungblud">Yungblud</a>的简短客串。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/frank-carter-interview-download-2024-sex-pistol-shows-3767041">弗兰克卡特说性手枪是对政府“废除社区理念”的反应</a><br /></strong></li></ul><p>这场演出于周二晚上（8 月 13 日）举行，是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sex-pistols-and-frank-carter-announce-extra-london-never-mind-the-bollocks-show-3763755">他们在伦敦布什大厅举行的三场演出中</a>的第一场，门票全部售完，卡特和性手枪乐团的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/glen-matlock">格伦·马特洛克</a>、保罗·库克和史蒂夫·琼斯在它的全部。</p><p>虽然他们没有按时间顺序播放专辑的曲目列表，但他们确实播放了每首歌曲，包括他们翻唱的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-stooges">The Stooges</a>的《No Fun》。</p><p>其中一个引人注目的时刻是 1977 年经典歌曲《God Save The Queen》的演绎，这首歌不仅由 Yungblud 即兴出演，而且卡特将歌词改为“ <em>God Save the King</em> ”。</p><p>继《Liar》之后、《Submission》之前，这首朋克热门歌曲在曲目列表中排名第八，新主唱对这首朋克歌曲进行了改编，以反映现任英国君主查理三世国王。</p><p>查看下面的演出片段和完整演出列表。 </p><p><iframe title="Sex Pistols ft Frank Carter (&amp; Yungblud) “God Save the Queen”于 2024 年 8 月 13 日在伦敦布什大厅现场直播" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/vxHHGlPlMTo?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe title="Sex Pistols ft Frank Carter “EMI” 于 2024 年 8 月 13 日在伦敦布什大厅现场直播" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/0RSFi2tU2dU?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="性手枪壮举。弗兰克·卡特“尸体”在伦敦布什大厅现场演出" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/oTNQNwLD5M0?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><h2> <strong>Sex Pistols 和 Frank Carter 8 月 13 日的演出名单是：</strong></h2><p> <strong>1.《阳光下的假期》</strong><br /> <strong>2.《十七岁》</strong><br /> <strong>3.“纽约”</strong><br /> <strong>4.“相当空缺”</strong><br /> <strong>5.“身体”</strong><br /> <strong>6.《你没有错吗》</strong><br /> <strong>7.“骗子”</strong><br /> <strong>8.“God Save the Queen”（歌词更改为“God Save The King”，并由 Yungblud 客串）</strong><br /> <strong>9.“提交”</strong><br /> <strong>10.“卫星”</strong><br /> <strong>11.“没有感情”</strong><br /> <strong>12.“百代”</strong><br /> <strong>13.“问题”</strong><br /> <strong>14.《No Fun》（The Stooges 封面）</strong><br /> <strong>15.“英国的无政府状态”</strong></p><p>宣布这些演出是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/frank-carter-sex-pistols-london-bush-hall-3779738">为了为历史悠久的牧羊人丛林场馆筹集资金</a>。 7 月下旬，据透露，由于一些众筹和 Sex Pistols 演出的成功，伦敦独立场馆将继续为未来几个月制定计划。 “Never Mind The Bollocks”演出的所有收益都用于帮助该场馆的长期文化输出。</p><p>在此之前，该场馆的未来受到了威胁，而且近几个月来，它永久关闭的可能性似乎越来越大。例如，今年早些时候，该公司透露<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/crowdfunder-launched-to-save-live-music-at-londons-legendary-bush-hall-3595570">需要通过众筹筹集 42,000 英镑，</a>以防止失去音乐地位。</p><p>谈到这座历史悠久的场馆受到威胁时， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/frank-carter-interview-download-2024-sex-pistol-shows-3767041">卡特在 2024 年下载节上接受<em>NME</em>采访</a>时表示，支持布什大厅等草根场馆是他一直以来最关心的事业。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C8UcK-mvEYA/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.